Title: Flamenco Meets Fado
DateModified: '2019-02-26'
DatePublished: '2019-02-26'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/flamenco-meets-fado
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Bryan Douglas
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: "Flamenco guitarist from Seattle travels to Portugal to find the best Fado artists\
  \ in Lisboa. On this journey we discover some hidden gems of reastaurants and late\
  \ night spots.  We will also encounter some of Portugal\u2019s finest musicians,\
  \ hear their stories, and hopefully find a mentor."
